pros:
Good training environment, especially for Physicians;
Excellent Employee Health Benefits;
Is getting better about rewarding the good ideas of its employees

cons:
A very "top down" management structure;
Also a very large organization, and growth is getting out of hand (too many times the left hand doesn't know what the right hand is doing and the right hand seems determined to keep the  left hand in the dark); bureaucracy often gets in the way of getting the job done.

I have worked at the Clinic for nearly 20 years, and when I came there, it was a wonderful place to work.  Now, not so much.
